{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1681-12_302"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Cerémonie faite à Lile en Flandre par les Chevaliers de S. Lazare]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", décembre 1681 [tome 13], p. 302-311."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Mercredy 17. de ce mois M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de la Rabliere, Grand Prieur pour la Flandre, de l’Ordre de Nostre-Dame de Mont-Carmel, & de Saint Lazare de Jerusalem, fit faire une tres-pompeuse Solemnité de la Feste de ce Saint, dans l’Eglise des Peres Carmes de Lile. On l’avoit ornée des plus belles Tapisseries de la Ville, & dans un lieu des plus apparens estoit le Portrait du Roy, Grand Maître de cet Ordre, & au dessous, celuy de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": " de Louvoys qui en est le Grand Vicaire. Il y avoit des lumieres en si grand nombre, qu’on peut dire qu’il estoit presque infiny. La Solemnité commença le jour précedent aux premieres Vespres que l’on chanta en Musique. Tous les Commandeurs & Chevaliers des Villes voisines y assisterent, & furent placez sur deux Estrades par M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[4]", "text": " le Conseiller Turpin qui faisoit la Charge de Maistre des Ceremonies. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[4]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[4]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[5]", "text": " du Mets, Gouverneur de la Citadelle, ne s’y trouva point, non plus que M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[5]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[5]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[6]", "text": " le Chevalier de la Trousse. Ce dernier estoit malade, & M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[6]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[6]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[7]", "text": " du Mets estoit occupé à la visite de l’Artillerie du Roy. Il y avoit treize Commandeurs, sçavoir."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de la Rabliere, Maréchal de Camps aux Armées du Roy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " de Saint Silvestre, Mestre de Camp, & Inspecteur de la Cavalerie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[2]", "text": " Rosamel, Capitaine Lieutenant des Gens-d’Armes de Flandre, Mestre de Camp."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[2]", "text": " d’Avejan, Commandant aux Gardes qui sont à Lile."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[2]", "text": " S. Germain de la Bretesche, Commandant d’un Bataillon des Gardes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/text()[2]", "text": " de Fourrille, Capitaine aux Gardes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/text()[2]", "text": " des Alleurs, Capitaine aux Gardes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]/text()[2]", "text": " de la Motte, Major de la Citadelle de Lile."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]